  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    e-Application for UK compulsory insurance certificate (MSF 3241)
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  

  <div class="column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    Ship owners' form for electronic email applications to MCA for certification of evidence of bunker, tanker or passenger liability insurance.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

